FuncDef: The profile default command displays the default IOAM profile view. The profile default command displays the default IOAM profile view. By default, a profile named default is created after the IOAM view is created. This command is supported only on the CE6860-SAN, CE6866K, CE6866, CE6860-HAM, CE8850-SAN, CE8851K, CE8851-32CQ8DQ-P and CE8850-HAM.
